title: War of the Roses: She Followed Him to New Orleans
description: There's A LOT going on in this War of the Roses.  Jackie is suspicious of her boyfriend so she followed him on a boy's trip to New Orleans and confronted him about some things.  They worked it out but now he's being weird about her coming to their dog's training classes.  What is he up to?
